               <head>Collection of kabbalistic treatises</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85018546" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>A collection of kabbalistic treatises. </summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="visible">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="141v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Ginat egoz</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">גנת אגוז</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/88057479">Gikatilla, Joseph ben Abraham</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/88057479">ג'קטילה, יוסף בן אברהם</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Incomplete at the beginning. Several of the leaves are misplaces, the proper order is indicated in almost every case by later notes at the bottom of the pages. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Corrections and additions in later handwriting are in a number of instances given in the margin. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="142r" to="143v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Sod Bat Sheva</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">סוד בת שבע</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/88057479" xml:lang="en">Gikatilla, Joseph ben Abraham</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName key="viaf.org/viaf/88057479" xml:lang="he">ג'קטילה, יוסף בן אברהם</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="144r" to="251v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Otsar ha-kavod</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אוצר הכבוד</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/24783259">Abulafia, Todros ben Joseph, ha-Levi</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/24783259">אבולעפיה, טודרוס בן יוסף הלוי</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Includes commentaries on tractates Berakhot, Shabat, folio 180r; Megilah, folio193r; Ta῾anit, folio 199r; Ḥagigah, folio 205r; Rosh ha-Shanah, folio 216v; Sukah, folio 224r; Pesaḥim, folio 229r; Ḥulin, folio 234v; ῾Eruvin, folio 240r; Yevamot, folio 242r; Soṭah, folio 248r. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 145r-156v give a complete table of contents, which show that the manuscript originally contained also tractate Ketubot, Giṭin and Ḳidushin. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The entire number of smaller sections is given as 496, but there are occasional mistakes in enumeration. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
